snippet: On Thursday, a 1.4-acre patch of land on the Caloosahatchee River off the city of Fort Myers was gaveled away in an unusual Internet auction that featured the property.
abstract: Private island in the Caloosahatchee River off Fort Myers, Fla, is sold for the relatively modest sum of $258,000 in an Internet auction to an anonymous bidder.
lead_paragraph: On Thursday, a 1.4-acre patch of land on the Caloosahatchee River off the city of Fort Myers was gaveled away in an unusual Internet auction that featured the property.
